Ur ggar ara iman-ik di lketṛa n lehḍur ifeṛɣen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, xḍu-k seg-sen ; teẓriḍ belli țțawin-d anagar amennuɣ.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer Ṛebbi nețța i gḥekkmen ɣef yemdanen meṛṛa. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer leṛwaḥ-nsen i gewwḍen ɣer lekmal.
Meɛna aṭas seg wid iḍehṛen belli, mačči kan zdat-es, meɛna am akken d amcafeɛ daɣen ɣef yura di tira iqedsen : Sbeddeɣ-k iwakken aț-țedṛu yid-es ma yella tedṛa d amezwaru.
S wakka, yedṛa-d wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Seddan-agi ț-țagi i d yețmeslayen seg yemxalafen akk-d tutlayin nniḍen.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Yuɣal d lemtel kan ɣef waṭas n lɛaddat n yemdanen n ddunit.
Di leǧwahi-nni, yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n lqanun s ɣuṛ Qayṣeṛ ameqqran ; yefka lameṛ ad țțujerrden imezdaɣ n temdint n Lquds akk-d wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi.
Acḥal d abrid i t-idemmer uṛuḥani-agi ɣer temdint n Biri. Deg-s, acḥal ɣeṣbeɣ melmi ara tecɛel !
M'ara d-iṣuḍ waḍu seg usammer teqqaṛem ad iḥmu lḥal ; d ayen i d-ideṛṛun daɣen.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n tmes ;
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer wexxam n wid yesselmaden lekdeb i gḥemmlen ad sɛun kra n yemdanen.
Atan wamek ara t-tɛeqlem : aț-țafem llufan yețțel, yeṭṭes di lmedwed, mkul aɛeqqa n uxerḍel, iɛebba lehlakat-nsen, aṭas daɣen i gebnan s ufella kan.
Akken daɣen i glaq ad xedment tilawin, ad ilint s llebsa isseṭren, ad sɛunt lḥeṛma d neyya, ur țzewwiqent acebbub-nsent, ur țcebbiḥent iman-nsent s ddheb,
Ma d kunwi tḥeqṛem igellil ! Tqudṛem imeṛkantiyen, wid i ten-yețṛaǧun ur kcimen ara ɣer daxel n tilawin, aț-țilim d ayla-k s wayes ara tenneḥcamen. S wakka aț-țesbeddeḍ d iɣed n temtunt ( iɣes ) n temtunt ( iɣes ) n temtunt ( iɣes !
Iḍaṛṛen-nsen țɣawalen iwakken ad ssizlen llebsa-nsen iwakken ad ssizlen ijehlen wiyaḍ, ad sɛun ayen ara ḥwiǧen.
Ur nezmir ara a nwi-d lemtel-agi a d-sbeggnen iman-nsen ; lameɛna xḍut i tissit n temtunt ( iɣes ) ara d-yeǧǧaren medden ɣef ddemma n lɛaddat-agi, neɣ m'ulac ad qqimen yid-sen.
tella dinna lḥila n ddheb i deg sseṛɣayen lebxuṛ akk-d usenduq n leɛqed iṛuccen s ddheb. Zdaxel n usenduq-agi yella uɛekkaz-nni n Haṛun yeǧǧuǧgen, illa daɣen aqbuc iččuṛen ț-țamanna akk-d teblaḍin i deg uran lumuṛat n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lɛid n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), i deg yețɛicin di ddnub akk-d yir tikli, iṛuccen s idammen n ddheb akk-d luḍu ; ma d zzit akk-d ddheb ɣef tikciwin i d-ițfeggiyen, s wezṛu akk-d ukubri.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi, ula d keččini ț-țmeslayt n tideț, seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Atah wayen yuklalen ad yili d sebba n uɣelluy i wid ixedmen ayen akk i d-tenna ccariɛa,
Axaṭer ilaq ad yili wayen ara d-nini : ilaq ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d wiyaḍ a ten-id-yerr ɣer webrid neɣ akken ilaq, meɛna ad yefk tazmert s wayes ara nemmeslay iman-nsen.
Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Di yal taswiɛt, s wul yeṣfan, mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ) tamtunt ( iɣes ) yellan di tmurt n Selyan.
Ayen i d-ițbegginen belli d ṛṛasul i lliɣ, llant daɣen wid iteṭṭfen deg-s, axaṭer ṭṭfet di liman i sɛan di Lmasiḥ.
Daymi i glaq aț-țxelṣem tabzert i lḥukuma, axaṭer wid ițdebbiṛen deg wannect-agi, xeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken i t-id yenna Sidi Ṛebbi.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet.
Imi tessawḍeḍ tira iqedsen s wul yeṣfan, acḥal ɛlayeḍ aṭas aya segmi semḥet s tefru temsalt-agi, yerna ilaq a d-nbeggen acḥal nebɣa a k-walin akk-d uselmed-agi !
Ma d win ur neqbil ara ad yili d ameqqran m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, tesselmadeḍ akken ilaq ad yili d ameqqran n tejmaɛt n watmaten.
Llan kra n yemdanen slan s wayagi, ilaq-aɣ a nemmeslay s lefɛayel, iwakken imdanen meṛṛa ad fehment, iwakken ad rnun iman-nsen d wid iḍehṛen, iwakken ur tekksen ara wayen ara s-d-beggnen liman-nsen.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
axaṭer deg wussan-nni, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt ur nesɛi lmeɛna, llan gar-asen wid ihelken lbeṛs ṣeffun di tudrin neɣ di mkul amkan ; wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ḥeṛsen-t seg wasmi i t-nɣan.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Sheggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset iman-is aț-țeɣli ɣer temdint n Lud. Tella gar-asent tijmaɛin n leɛṭeṛ yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen, yeɛni annect-agi ɣef ddemma n tesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ.
Tusa-d yiwet n taǧǧalt tigellilt tessers sin iṣurdiyen yesɛan azal n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa.
Di temdint n Ifasus iwumi ur yețṛuḥu sebba s wayes i d-yṛuḥ ujelkaḍ di tmurt n Yahuda yellan ț-țamurt n Imelɛas, issenǧuyel-is d imdukkal nniḍen di lexṣaṣ.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet. Ihi m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, ilaq ad yili d aweḥḥi-nni deg yiwen uɛeqqa kan n yired.
M'ara tețnejmaɛem yețțili lxilaf gar-awen, tețṛuḥum ɣer wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken ad frun tilufa-nwen !
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Imi teṭṭfem di ṭṭlam i gella ; ula d kunwi aț-țilim di leɛtab di tmazirt n igenwan iwakken aț-țilim ț-țaɛebbuḍ deg waggurt-nkunt,
Llant gar-aneɣ acḥal d abrid i t-iɛedda si lebḥeṛ ɣer tmurt n Maṣer, si dderya n imawlan-nsen, i gextaṛ Sidna Ibṛahim akk-d Isḥaq, Yeɛqub ț-țilawin-nsen.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, mačči ɣef ddemma n wat Isṛail i gețțili ț-țaɛkumt ula i yiwen.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ccṛeɛ ;
Axaṭer mkul aɛeqqa n yired yeɣlin deg wakal m'ara d-teḥyu, ur s-tewqiɛ ara lmeɛna d acu yellan di lexla : ad sneg neɣ deg wezṛu neɣ di lebḥuṛ armi ț-țeṛwum i d-ițfeggiyen.
Wiyaḍ daɣen țwaqehṛen s ustehzi, s ujelkkaḍ, s snasel d leḥbus.
Tafaska n izimer n leslak tqeṛb-ed i gellan di lemḥayen i gɛedda si lexla. M'ara d-yas Lmasiḥ a d-isbeggen iman-is belli ɣelṭen ɣef wayen yeɛnan Tafaska n izimer n leslak.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, wid ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad amnen s Sidi Ṛebbi ; ṭṭfen di leǧwameɛ n wat Isṛail.
Taṣebḥit, tewweḍ-ed lmuqeddem i deg ara d-sɛeddin lɛid n Tfaska, daymi i țheggin imensi n Tfaska.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, lameɛna sɛan daɣen tazmert s wayes ara tedṛu d uquṛan iṭij.
Mmugreɣ-ed acḥal n wuguren m'ara tsafaṛeɣ : isaffen iweɛṛen, imakaren deg iberdan, lxuf di temdinin n lɛid n Tfaska. Lameɛna tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen nnejmaɛen deg yiḍ n lɛid n Tfaska.
Ma d wid akk yețmuqulen di lebḥeṛ, ṣubben-d ɣuṛ-es kra n wayen yedṛan, slet-ed ɣer dagi zdat n wayen ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Imi walan akkenni ur zmiren ara a t-ssiwḍen ɣer beṛṛa, ur zmiren ara ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ; s wakka i sen-d-yewweḍ leɛtab ameqqran irac n temdint n Ludikus.
M'ara d-yas yiwen seg-wen ad awḍen ɣer temdint n Jafa. Llan deg-s aṭas n yemdanen i d-ilulen si lexla, zzuɣṛen-nsen d iquḍaṛen, iderɣalen, ikeṛṛusen tezdayen akk-d iqettalen,
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegrawliwin neɣ si cceṛq d lɣeṛb, ilaq aț-țawḍem ɣer usammer, ur d-yekki ara seg wayen yellan d ṭṭlam.
A wen-d-yețțunefk ayen yelhan tețțaseḍ d wayen yuklalen lmut, ad ilin d imeṭṭḍen ɣer igenni.
Imi Brisila d Akilas xeddmen iqiḍunen am Bulus, yeqqim ɣuṛ-sen xeddmen s tdukli, ur xeddmet ara lxilaf ger yemdanen, yerna tzemrem aț-țuxem ula d kunwi deg waman iwakken aț-țilim di tafat.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
A lḥakem ameqqran ! S uḍebbaṛ-ik yelhan i d-yers lxiṛ d lehna ɣef tmurt-agi ! Ɣef wayagi, a Filiks ameqqran, ncekkeṛ-ik meṛṛa di mkul amkan ;
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n lɛiqab i wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
